subject: Basketball

College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Keisha Hampton scored 27 points, Felicia Chester had a career-high 24 and No. 22 DePaul routed No. 3 Stanford in Chicago, denying Cardinal Coach Tara VanDerveer her 800th career victory.
